The TestNG <test name="ConformanceTests"> block's
<groups><dependencies depends-on="core" name="systemfeatures"/></dependencies>
declaration in src/main/jlib/testng.xml mechanically cascaded SKIP from the
failed Core @Tests to all SystemFeatures @Tests. This is the runtime semantic
that the unit-test layer (VerifyTestNGSuiteDependency.java, 4 @Tests for
structural lint) cannot exercise — only end-to-end execution against a
sabotaged IUT can prove the depends-on wiring actually triggers SKIP at
runtime.

